Package com.esri.gpt.catalog.harvest.repository Description

Harvest repository requests.

Contains all the possible requests on harvest repository: selecting, updating/adding, deleting, testing. It also includes all the classes required to invoke such request.

See Also:
HrSelectRequest, HrUpdateRequest, HrDeleteRequest, HrHarvestRequest, HrTestRequest
